{"tid":413091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi你班所謂正能樣唔好再累死人","createTime":"2017-09-25T08:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T07:50:46.000Z","uid":137719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eec2e3ed36bf9ba1839e74b74eaae3977d256ff6","tid":413091,"uid":137719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/agentofchangehk/videos/757477867793413/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fagentofchangehk%2Fvideos%2F757477867793413%2F&d=yT8x7Aq%2F5ss%2Bamssk%2Fwf8Yzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c02209ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/agentofchangehk/videos/757477867793413/</a><br />\n<br />\n個個禮拜都有中學生跳樓自殺，聽完啲社工講之後發現鬼唔系成日有班所謂正能樣同班想自殺既人鳩up，懶醒以為氹人兩句就可以幫人減少負能樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實諗唔開既人唔系想人鳩up氹下，反而系想有人可以比佢拎件事出黎一齊傾，俾人了解下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2781e382c1d56efc0f172e53e086a3816572a32d","tid":413091,"uid":137719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到今日又死五件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298a4d59940e3e31141bc45536da99bcaf1ebd43","tid":413091,"uid":148174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"系你老母咩"},{"pid":"436dcf8c91034db97a114f709bf043542327cdc2","tid":413091,"uid":137726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:45:39.000Z","msg":"好心班仆街正撚樣就唔好再懶撚係好心咁講乜野夠膽去死唔夠膽面